item.description: Linnea Linnea Future coder and sleep-enthusiast. My name is Linnea and I am 1/3 of team Game of Code. My goal in life is to become a talanted coder whose good at solving problems. I have basic knowledge in some coding-languages, which you can find on the About us page if that interests you. I started to learn my first language at 17 years old which was html and css, and from there I went on to learn the basics in a few more and to use diffrent tools.
